{"tid":226611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓稱倘爆核戰　第一個就打日本","createTime":"2017-05-02T15:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T14:37:44.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e4c759130df4713801a04c6c7c388fa012bab6","tid":226611,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"北韓稱倘爆核戰　日本或最先遭殃<br />\n北韓《勞動新聞》譴責日本派出海上自衛隊，與美國航母開展聯合訓練，煽動朝鮮半島局勢，假如發生核戰，作為美軍後勤和出擊基地的日本，可能最先被輻射烏雲覆蓋。<br />\n<br />\n報道說日本衝在鼓吹朝鮮半島危機的最前面，形容對方以此作為推進軍國化的絕佳機會，提醒日本如果考慮本國利益，應努力促進和平解決半島問題。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1328229-20170502.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1328229-20170502.htm&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2e85c26b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1328229-20170502.htm&h=95169897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1328229-20170502.htm</a><br />\n日本太多事了 一於炸到佢沉沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3623c527035fcd344028ec224247cf8050aeb6f0","tid":226611,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"947c61a7c196473e94806917df998463d2fe4730","tid":226611,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"受傷的總是日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96016c72c77727442a1dfebe587e022a3d5b3070","tid":226611,"uid":68009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:28:44.000Z","msg":"hoball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e4dcf247cca6c7bb636eb5fb9ab7471eedfdda","tid":226611,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"Ho ball"},{"pid":"affc227cff005990511859ee144ad581e1d3e59a","tid":226611,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"434c6b797c01df1149caead483ce00ffdcf77138","tid":226611,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d29030bd622202fa9a71413a41c5c71aae76d9a","tid":226611,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"北泡導彈有成功飛過日本海咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57935cb6173a465150333b137d69186ad2f35c1c","tid":226611,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T15:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北泡導彈有成功飛過日本海咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上可以飛到去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecd47e3c4f0b98638d4ee7162ab94304cd09dfc","tid":226611,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>北泡導彈有成功飛過日本海咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上可以飛到去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得有一年飛越過日本, 跌左落海<br />\n<br />\n跟住有一個負責防空既官員自殺左"},{"pid":"beecdb7002e741bdf9f4a9dc00c3ddfe640d9a52","tid":226611,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"最近金仔嘅細國，而飛彈又大機會射到嘅得兩個：南韓同日本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔打呢兩個，唔通打俄羅斯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定打外蒙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e37f8097bb2f10675ce2a92d1def5e8f28402a","tid":226611,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"793e55582dd7c602552e2c19a48ec218ec1a734f","tid":226611,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近金仔嘅細國，而飛彈又大機會射到嘅得兩個：南韓同日本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔打呢兩個，唔通打俄羅斯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定打外蒙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係你平時好喜歡打你D鄰居??<br />\n見邊個住得近, 就打柒佢??"},{"pid":"29c703898f78d99b2ec75c42cd87900ebcf222ca","tid":226611,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南泡咁易炸都唔打打日本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家陣北韓學緊慈禧太后, 向八國宣戰<br />\n<br />\n金仔:「如美國出手, 我會核平美國」<br />\n「我將會核平南韓」<br />\n「我會將核彈射向中國」<br />\n「如有核戰, 第一個射日本」<br />\n<br />\n暫時已經向左四個國家宣戰<br />\n仲有四個名單"},{"pid":"d5810dfcb1f41483b8d6f16d82f43277a3d2b477","tid":226611,"uid":92714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南泡咁易炸都唔打打日本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南泡太易，打黎side鳩氣<br />\n打完驚動到日本/美軍<br />\n之後打日本相對難好多<br />\n<br />\n一開始打日本係一個好明智既決定<br />\n之後再翻兜南泡都唔會增加難度"},{"pid":"9974439f3a15c5b4901c67d8c6d5c83373f44ecd","tid":226611,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f6d127b674527251f65c99956a3fb32dc2a7544","tid":226611,"uid":92714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"前題，俄羅b/支那唔出手"},{"pid":"e0bb13ac3efd79576b5dbbb9a3663e72457879a2","tid":226611,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近金仔嘅細國，而飛彈又大機會射到嘅得兩個：南韓同日本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔打呢兩個，唔通打俄羅斯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定打外蒙？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係你平時好喜歡打你D鄰居??<br />\n見邊個住得近, 就打柒佢??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地發爛渣呀，之前成日話炸南韓，無睇頭，依家轉個對象，希望有人留意返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b451594ce2e3948936c64f7dcdd06f711d5a57","tid":226611,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>北泡導彈有成功飛過日本海咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n理論上可以飛到去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得有一年飛越過日本, 跌左落海<br />\n<br />\n跟住有一個負責防空既官員自殺左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老豆豆，我係支國都借啲意俾日本捱一兩刀先，<br />\n再出兵搞9北韓，反正出師有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd3fabe2db5becfa97cb7193c625f8d0cb69eeb","tid":226611,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"打啦<br />\n日本即刻修憲出兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7869e9d56bd6254518796e1107144492d044d68d","tid":226611,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"安倍不知幾想你打佢<br />\n一打佢就有名義修戰爭法.."},{"pid":"3776ae0636327127db2bb7c8cfda2fe67b8079e5","tid":226611,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南泡咁易炸都唔打打日本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n家陣北韓學緊慈禧太后, 向八國宣戰<br />\n<br />\n金仔:「如美國出手, 我會核平美國」<br />\n「我將會核平南韓」<br />\n「我會將核彈射向中國」<br />\n「如有核戰, 第一個射日本」<br />\n<br />\n暫時已經向左四個國家宣戰<br />\n仲有四個名單</blockquote><br />\n慈禧太后係對全世界宣戰，<br />\n不過最後得八個打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ea18ccf0dab07ec0e1cb7cf0a6822f93c6b6b5","tid":226611,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好啦 炸中國算啦<br />\n我仲要去日本架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炸中國既話<br />\n中國一定唔會係戰敗國<br />\n但如果北韓炸日本<br />\n仲有一絲既希望拖埋中國落水做戰敗國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f1cd66a08790db06593971b61465543bdaffa3","tid":226611,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"又話開戰打南泡先<br />\n而家又改，佢想點架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494072aa00867d1549cca1a446dc07b7cc16ac6e","tid":226611,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>南泡咁易炸都唔打打日本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南泡太易，打黎side鳩氣<br />\n打完驚動到日本/美軍<br />\n之後打日本相對難好多<br />\n<br />\n一開始打日本係一個好明智既決定<br />\n之後再翻兜南泡都唔會增加難度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實北韓選擇打仗, 已經唔係一個明智決定<br />\n因為無論打邊個國家, 下場都係死"}]}